                    <Label  Padding="5,5,5,5"  HorizontalTextAlignment="Center" TextColor="White"  FontFamily="Cooper Hewitt" Text="The exclusive lounging destination in Dubai. Located on the 7th floor of the Conrad Hotel dubai with three different exotic venues to choose from along with a breathtaking view overlooking the Sheik Zayed Road. Did we mention our menu is to die for? Our exciting menu is curated with delicious dishes from all over the world along with exotic cocktails and shisha flavors alongside upbeat playlists created by our DJs. It has  grown to become one of the popular nightlife destinations in Dubai. The trendy spot has  become a hub for socializing &amp; celebrations. Open from 7 pm to 3 am, 7 days a week." HorizontalOptions="Start" VerticalOptions="Center" />
