                    <Label  Padding="10"  HorizontalTextAlignment="Center"   TextColor="White"  FontFamily="Cooper Hewitt" Text=" Serving a wide selection of delicious food and exotic beverages, Secret garden is an ideal place to unwind. Most of our exclusive events happen here - Secret Sundays, Uptown Mondays, Chica's Night and many more. Not to miss out on our resident ladies man, Mr. Monkey, who is a very stylish golden monkey. He wears black shades and golden chains cause he's cool like that!"></Label>
                </StackLayout>
            </Frame>


            <Label  Margin="10,0,0,0"  HorizontalTextAlignment="Center" FontAttributes="Bold" FontSize="Title" TextColor="#b29476" FontFamily="Cooper Hewitt"  Text="RED ROOM" HorizontalOptions="Center" VerticalOptions="Center" />

